oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Dam No. 8, Thompson Creek Watershed, a floodwater retarding structure located in Weakley County, Tenn. An overall view of the dam, revealing good slopes and an excellent sodding of Bermuda grass.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The second structure was constructed July 21, 1959, and was completed October 29, 1959.
